Package com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.definitions.description

package com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.definitions.description

This packages includes different types of Descriptions that contain meta information about classes, methods und parameters, similar to reflections.

Descriptions are created by an implementation of Descriptions and are used in many places of this framework, resulting in the possible avoidance of java reflections.
